  "instructions": [
    "Heat a non-stick pan to a medium-high temperature (190°C).",
    "Mix matcha powder and ghee in a bowl to form a uniform paste.",
    "Add paneer cheese to the matcha-ghee paste and mix until fully coated.",
    "Coat the paneer mixture in a mixture of all-purpose flour, garam masala, cumin powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Heat a non-stick skillet to a medium-high temperature (190°C) and deep-fry the paneer mixture in batches until golden brown.",
